title: GeneticistIntro
---
<<once>>
    Geneticist: Hello stanger. I saw your Dirigible float by my viewport. We don't get many tourists. 
    Geneticist: What brings you all the way out here to the very periphery of civilization?
<<else>>
    Geneticist: Hello again, Stanger please don't make a habit of wasting my time. What do you want?
    -> Am I still a stranger? We've talked before.
    -> Sorry to bother you, I'll leave you alone.
        <<jump End01>>
<<endonce>>

-> Well, I had a family member pass with property not far from here.
-> I thought I'd get out into the wilderness and try my hand at prospecting.
Geneticist: Well, I'm sorry to hear that, Mr. Well, sit, please. How can I help you?
-> Well, my sister, the relation I spoke of, I thought to ask here at the closest outpost. Did you ever meet her?
Geneticist: 
