title: FabrikatorIntro
---
<<declare $sawTheMine = false>>
<<declare $hasPassedOut = false>>
Fabrikator: What can I do for you, sir?
<<if $sawTheMine>>
-> I saw the mine across the valley. What do you know about it?
<<endif>>
-> I'm just passing through. Nothing for now, thanks.
    <<jump End01>>
