title: HypolitaWillConverse
---
Hypolita: Ah, hello. Clancy tells me you've been useful.
<<complete_objective DialogueCommands "SpeakWithHypolita000">>
Hypolita: Says you have some questions about the outpost? 
Hypolita: Well, I have manned this research post since its construction 10 years ago.
-> Ask about Sister
Hypolita: Yes, I knew your sister. She would supply us on contracts from time to time.
Hypolita: A psychologist from the Prime settlement, I recall?
-> That's right.
-> How did you know her?
    Hypolita: She had a strong scientific curiosity and we crossed paths living and working
    Hypolita: in this valley. She had questions about the Cores and what I thought the Rush 
    Hypolita: was doing to the ecosystem in this region. I shared my findings and she shared her views.
Hypolita: Well, I remember those months. I saw her a few times. She was planning a trip to the east.
-> What is in the east?
Hypolita: Not much in the way of civilization. A couple of mines. 
Hypolita: Boundless wilderness. So much that has been seen only from orbit.
Hypolita: I suspect she met some unknown fate in the east.
-> Is there anything else you remember about her trip to the east?
Hypolita: She mentioned a man named Fulmen who would accompany her. 
Hypolita: A guide of sorts. A man who was here long before the boomtowns of the Rush years.
-> Thank you, doctor. I will consider what you've said.
Hypolita: Clancy mentioned you harvested some cores for us? Much obliged.
<<add_objective DialogueCommands "ReturnCoresToHypolita">>
<<activate_objective DialogueCommands "ReturnCoresToHypolita">>
Hypolita: I will take them now. As you know, they are illegal outside of research use.
-> Yes, doctor, here they are.
    <<jump GaveHypolitaCores>>
-> Actually, I think I'll hold on to them.
    <<jump DontGiveHypolitaCores>>
===

title: GaveHypolitaCores
---
<<remove_player_item DialogueCommands "BasicInnerCoreStandard">>
<<remove_player_item DialogueCommands "BasicInnerCoreStandard">>
<<complete_objective DialogueCommands "ReturnCoresToHypolita">>
<<add_objective DialogueCommands "TalkWithClancy05">>
<<activate_objective DialogueCommands "TalkWithClancy05">>
<<add_objective DialogueCommands "VisitCoreTrader">>
<<activate_objective DialogueCommands "VisitCoreTrader">>
Hypolita: Thank you, sir. Here are the coordinates of the mining camps I mentioned.
===

title: DontGiveHypolitaCores
---
Hypolita: You mean to sell them... I don't have to tell you it's illegal, I'm sure you know.
Hypolita: You've helped me with these samples so I'll not report you... 
// <<sigh DialogueCommands>>
Hypolita: The whole planet disregarded people like me, with me during the RUSH 8 years ago.
Hypolita: I had been here years before then, mind you, studying the alien life on this planet.
Hypolita: It's human nature I suppose, but then some would call me traitor to my species.
-> I should go...
    <<jump End01>>
-> So why did you stay?
Hypolita: You don't think I'm all the way out here by choice, do you? I'm an old environmentalist.
Hypolita: So I'll ask you again, you're sure you want to try and sell them? The market isn't what it was during the RUSH...
-> You're right. I will leave them with you after all.
    <<jump GaveHypolitaCores>>
-> I'm sorry but yes, doctor. I'm running out of money as it is.
    // <<adopt_hostile_pose DialogueCommands>>
    <<make_objective_inactive DialogueCommands "ReturnCoresToHypolita">>
    <<add_objective DialogueCommands "TalkWithClancy05">>

Hypolita: I see... In that case, I would like to get back to my work. I'm dissappointed but not surprised.
===